I&#39;ve been meaning to ask Ken more details about how he produced the
speciation graphs in his papers.  Is that speciation visualization
built into your release, Ken?  Is this what Tyler&#39;s referring to?

&gt; I noticed a good speciation picture in the Yahoo group
